~ HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language
~ HTML is a markup language that web developers use to structure and
  describe the content of a webpage (not programming language).
~ What does the markup language means is we use the language to describe something.
  ~ in case HTML, we do describe content using elements.
~ HTML consists of elements that describe different types of content:
  paragraphs, links, headings, images, videos, etc.
